Decentralised Escrow Service

Covid Escrow Service is an effective way for Buyers to eliminate their risk in transactions with Vendors and ensure they are fully protected. We provide escrow services for a range of carding services, including virtual goods and physical goods.

Officially, Clearnet Escrow Services does not support illegal DarkNet transactions and in many cases both the Buyer and Vendor anonymity is breached. Due to the FBIs seizure of the original Silk Road, and many more markets, we adopt a decentralised escrow service.

Covid Market provides an anonymous escrow-like behavior through manual payouts. This gives Buyers influence over payouts, with the ability to delay payouts to Vendors accounts for up to 30 days. Learn More
